HEADWORD: Chef
<hw>Chef</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A chief or head person.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The head cook of large establishment, as a club, a
family, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Her.)</fld> <def>Same as <er>Chief</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

